name: D-Feet
description: D-Feet is an easy-to-use D-bus debugger. It's used to check the operating procedures of D-Bus interface and methods of call interface. It can display all the objects, signals and methods provided by service, and the method call can be achieved through it.

en_US.description: D-Feet is an easy-to-use D-bus debugger. It's used to check the operating procedures of D-Bus interface and methods of call interface. It can display all the objects, signals and methods provided by service, and the method call can be achieved through it.
en_US.name: D-Feet

zh_CN.description: D-Feet是一个易于使用D-bus调试器，D-Feet用来检查D-bus接口的运行程序和调用接口的方法。可以显示service提供的所有对象、信号和方法，还可以通过它实现方法调用。
zh_CN.name: D-Feet
